# Gemini Agent Project Context

This document provides context for the Gemini agent to understand the project
structure, conventions, and key technologies.

## Guidelines

- Use `pnpm` as package manager
- Only excode when asked to do so
- Don't install dependencies. List them in the end for manual installation
- You are free to use `pnpm run typecheck` to check for type errors
- You are free to use `pnpm run lint:fix` to fix linting errors (prefer over
  manual fixes)
- You are free to use `pnpm run lint` to check for linting errors

## Key Project Patterns & Technologies

### Frameworks

- Vue 3 + VueUse (UI framework + composables)
- Nuxt 4 + Nuxt UI (UI components + SSSR)
- tRPC (type safe remote procedure calls)
- tus (resumable file uploads)
- Drizzle ORM (PostgreSQL)
- LangChain + Langgraph (AI agents)

