## Project File Structure

```
├───docker-compose.yml              # Defines services for Docker, like the database
├───drizzle.config.ts               # Configuration for Drizzle ORM
├───eslint.config.mjs               # ESLint configuration for linting
├───nuxt.config.ts                  # Nuxt.js framework configuration
├───Procfile                        # Process file for Heroku deployment
├───README.md                       # Project README file
├───tsconfig.json                   # TypeScript configuration
├───.github/                        # GitHub Actions workflows
├───app/                            # Frontend application (Vue/Nuxt)
│   ├───components/                 # Vue components
│   ├───pages/                      # Nuxt pages for routing
│   │   └───process/                # Page for process-related features
│   └───plugins/
│       └───trpc.ts                 # tRPC client-side plugin (setups client-side tRPC)
├───server/
│   ├───api/
│   │   ├───trpc/                   # tRPC endpoint
│   │   ├───tus/                    # tus endpoint
│   │   └───webhooks/
│   │       └───stripe.post.ts      # Stripe webhook handler
│   ├───db/
│   │   ├───drizzle.ts              # Drizzle ORM instance and connection
│   │   ├───schema.ts               # Database schema definitions
│   │   └───migrations/             # Drizzle migration files
│   ├───graphs/                     # Langgraph related files
│   │   └───handlers/               # Langgraph node handlers
│   ├───trpc/                       # tRPC server setup and procedures
│   └───utils/
│       ├───asserts.ts              # Assertion utilities
│       ├───drizzle.ts              # Drizzle ORM utilities
│       ├───openai.ts               # OpenAI API utilities
│       ├───queues.ts               # Queue management utilities
│       ├───stripe.ts               # Stripe API utilities
│       ├───trpc.ts                 # tRPC utilities
│       └───tus.ts                  # TUS file upload utilities
└───shared/
    ├───types.d.ts                  # Shared TypeScript type definitions
    └───zods.ts                     # Zod schemas and types for validation
```
